    return -code error "

The gimp-dev port is now deprecated since the 2.3 release has come to an end.

Maybe we'll meet again when the 2.5 releases are going well.

Until then, please use either gimp (Batteries included - meta port) or gimp2 (just gimp) port.

Thank you for using gimp-dev

"
}

